_sText:
This is my 2nd orange map. The sides are mostly simmilar to each other. The weapons spawn on the ground. The cover are mostly crates, some of them are breakable. There are 12 spawnpoints for ct's and t's so maximum 24 players can play this map. Also the water is some barricade, so the distance is a bit longer sometimes.
v1.1: - added nav.-file made by chizbone - corrected a func_breakable glitch CREDITS: - offroad - chizbone (navfile)
Installation: extract to your maps folder in cstrike example: x:\program files\steam\yourusername\counterstrike source\cstrike\maps
See my other maps here
